      "question": "The speed of a boat in still water is 12 km/h. If it goes downstream at 15 km/h, what is the speed of the stream?",
      "options": [
        "2 km/h",
        "3 km/h",
        "4 km/h",
        "5 km/h"
      ],
      "explanation": "Downstream = boat speed + stream speed. 15 = 12 + stream. Stream = 3 km/h."
    },
    "hi": {
