  {
    "id": "gdmbs-0004",
    "correctOption": "A",
    "difficulty": "hard",
    "sourceYear": 2023,
    "en": {
      "question": "A boat covers 16 km upstream and 24 km downstream in 6 hours. It covers 12 km upstream and 36 km downstream in the same time. Find the speed of the stream.",
      "options": [
        "4 km/h",
        "3 km/h",
        "2 km/h",
        "5 km/h"
      ],
      "explanation": "Let US speed = x, DS speed = y. From equations: 16/x + 24/y = 6 and 12/x + 36/y = 6. Solving: y = 12, x = 4. Stream speed = (y-x)/2 = (12-4)/2 = 4 km/h."
    },
    "hi": {
      "question": "एक नाव 16 km धारा के प्रतिकूल और 24 km धारा के अनुकूल 6 घंटे में तय करती है। वह 12 km प्रतिकूल और 36 km अनुकूल समान समय में तय करती है। धारा की गति ज्ञात करें।",
      "options": [
        "4 km/h",
        "3 km/h",
        "2 km/h",
        "5 km/h"
      ],
      "explanation": "माना प्रतिकूल गति = x, अनुकूल गति = y। 16/x + 24/y = 6 और 12/x + 36/y = 6। हल करने पर: y = 12, x = 4। धारा की गति = (y-x)/2 = (12-4)/2 = 4 km/h।"
    }
  },
  {
