    "difficulty": "medium",
    "sourceYear": 2024,
    "en": {
      "question": "A boat takes 2 hours more to go 45 km upstream than to return downstream. If the speed of the stream is 3 km/h, find the speed of the boat in still water.",
      "options": [
        "10 km/h",
        "12 km/h",
        "14 km/h",
        "15 km/h"
      ],
      "explanation": "Let boat speed = x. 45/(x-3) - 45/(x+3) = 2. 45(x+3-x+3)/(x^2-9) = 2. 45x6/(x^2-9) = 2. 270 = 2x^2 - 18. 2x^2 = 288. x = 12 km/h."
    },
    "hi": {
      "question": "एक नाव को धारा के प्रतिकूल 45 km जाने में, अनुकूल लौटने की तुलना में 2 घंटे अधिक लगते हैं। यदि धारा की गति 3 km/h है, तो शांत जल में नाव की गति ज्ञात करें।",
      "options": [
        "10 km/h",
        "12 km/h",
        "14 km/h",
        "15 km/h"
      ],
      "explanation": "माना नाव की गति = x। 45/(x-3) - 45/(x+3) = 2। 45(x+3-x+3)/(x^2-9) = 2। 45×6/(x^2-9) = 2। 270 = 2x^2 - 18। 2x^2 = 288। x = 12 km/h।"
    }
  },
